ictions on freedom of movementdo little to stop the spread of Covid, while causing enormous harm.\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3210, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"scientific evidence\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"freedom\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3131}, {\"ngram\": \"the spread\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3171}, {\"ngram\": \"Covid\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3180}, {\"ngram\": \"enormous harm\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if a city really is somehow too disease-ridden to allow normal human interaction, it is also too disease-ridden to host the Games.\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3345, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a city\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3224}, {\"ngram\": \"normal human interaction\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3295}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Point 5 was inspired by the ridiculously oppressive Covid restrictions at the 2022 Beijing Games.\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Point\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3352}, {\"ngram\": \"the ridiculously oppressive Covid restrictions\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3417}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2022 Beijing Games\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will only occasionally be relevant.\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3483, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the others have broader applicability.\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the others\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3498}, {\"ngram\": \"broader applicability\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I also explained how the US and other liberal democracies could force the International Olympic Committee (IOC) to adopt these reforms: [N]one of these ideas are likely to be adopted by the notoriously corrupt International Olympic Committee.\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 355